Candidate Profile from Congressional Quarterly

Parris N. Glendening (D) of University Park

Incumbent - elected 1994

Born: June 11, 1942, Bronx, N.Y.

Education: Florida State U., B.A., 1964, M.A., 1965, Ph.D., 1967.

Military Service: None.

Occupation: Professor.

Family: Wife, Frances Anne Hughes; one child.

Religion: Roman Catholic.

Political Career: Hyattsville City Council, 1973-74; Prince George's County Council, 1974-82, chairman, 1980-81; Prince George's County executive, 1982-94.

Campaign Address: 6811 Kenilworth Ave., Suite 200, Riverdale, MD 20737

Telephone: (301) 887-1998

Fax: (301) 277-8415

E-mail: Not reported.

Web: Not reported.
